RasterFunctionTemplate.Name: GSSICB_Amplitude_Power_2SD
RasterFunctionTemplate.Description: Calculates gamma-0 power from the backscatter DN values of the Global Seasonal Sentinel-1 Interferometric Coherence and Backscatter datatset. A 2 Standard Deviation stretch is applied.

Function.Name: Stretch
Function.Description: Enhances an image by adjusting the range of values displayed. This does not alter the underlying pixel values. If a pixel has a value outside of the specified range, it will appear as either the minimum or maximum value.

Function.Name: Calculate Power
Function.Description: Calculates gamma-0 power from the backscatter DN values of the Global Seasonal Sentinel-1 Interferometric Coherence and Backscatter datatset.
